story.text: I got an early start today and was able to meditate. A rewarding experience. My throat still has a tickle and I should probably visit a doctor - but I am not going to.
I am watching Adelaide and Alexandra for the first time solo tonight. Very exciting.
Listening to more of Scale - I think the book may be as important as Huxley or Darwin's work on evolution. Fundamental scaling laws in nature will come to define the future, I think.
